Smurfs vs Zombies

Zombies rise out of the ground and follow the Smurf player character.
A max of 30 zombies spawn.
The game ends if the Zombie hits the player.
The player wins if all Zombies fall off the ledge.
(You can also see a game win state by pressing p, for testing purposes).

The player moves faster than the zombie, and move with WASD.
They jump with the right mouse button, and when in the jump state, zombies can’t harm them.

You can move the camera by holding down the left mouse button and moving the mouse.
Lastly, you can zoom in and out the camera with the “i” and “o” buttons respectively.  

